<span class="style26">
    
     <!-- stopped here -->
soliloquios del viento (2016)<br></span>
<span class="style28">for Talea Ensemble and EXAUDI<br>
six singers, bass flute, bass clarinet, tenor saxophone, percussion, piano, violin, viola, and cello
<center><span class="style27">Commissioned by Voix Nouvelles de la Fondation Royaumont<br>
World Premiere: Royaumont Abbey, France - September 9, 2016</span>
</center>
<br>
    <center>

</center>


	</td></tr>
    
